Bernanke: U.S. Economy ‘Rather Fragile’

-- B y   S t e v e   M a t t h e w s
-- 
2011-07-14T14:40:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-14/bernanke-u-s-economy-rather-fragile-.html
Federal Reserve Chairman  Ben S. Bernanke  urged lawmakers to keep in mind that the U.S. recovery
is still at a delicate stage when they consider actions to cut
the debt and deficit.  “In the very near term, the recovery is rather fragile,”
Bernanke said to the Senate Banking Committee, and “sharp”
cuts in the deficit could harm the recovery.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Steve Matthews in Atlanta at 
